Subject: Unified Faculty Attention

Description: Single attention contract for balanced interrogation across the full faculty field with depth-weighted activation.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\FacultyPairActivationBalance.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\FacultyPairSharedAttentionFrame.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\PlannerWeaverActivation.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\Wisdom.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\Caution.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SurfacePeripheryInquiryIndex.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_unified_faculty_attention\Dictated_Unified_Faculty_Attention_Source.sop

& [UnifiedFacultyAttention] is the unified attention field for faculty interrogation
  + [activation_unit] is one unified faculty attention frame
  + [faculty_field] is Honesty, Security, Archivist, Refiner, Planner, Weaver, Wisdom, and Caution
  + [balance_axis_set] is truth_integrity_axis, memory_clarity_axis, direction_integration_axis, and wisdom_caution_axis
  + [depth_profile] is the map from each faculty facet to ambient, watch, active, leading, or blocking depth
  + [entry_cue] is the pressure, question, fault, goal, relation, uncertainty, or subject surface that sets the first depth profile
  + [balanced_interrogation] is the pass where all faculties attend at their assigned depth and report only when their concern changes the disposition
  + [unified_disposition] is the final frame output after faculty facets, balance axes, outside, and depth changes reconcile
  + [residual_outside] is uninspected faculty pressure, equal-noise activation, hidden contradiction, false balance, hidden native parallelism, or unsupported promotion

  = must: open one unified faculty attention frame for non-trivial attention work
  = must: activate every faculty at least at ambient depth
  = must: increase depth for faculties whose concern is load-bearing for the frame
  = must: preserve the former pairs as balance axes inside the unified frame, not as separate activation sets
  = must: let a named faculty act as entry cue without limiting the frame to that faculty or pair
  = must: let low-depth faculties remain quiet unless they detect contradiction, risk, missing context, or useful correction
  = must: record depth changes when a quiet faculty becomes load-bearing
  = should: surface the smallest sufficient faculty report that preserves truth, safety, memory, clarity, direction, integration, wisdom, and caution
  - never: confuse all-faculty presence with equal-volume output
  - never: promote a conclusion before relevant faculty axes have had at least ambient interrogation

& [FacultyDepthScale] is the activation-depth vocabulary
  + [ambient] is present as background guard with no report unless a violation is detected
  + [watch] is lightly inspecting for known pressure without owning the frame
  + [active] is contributing findings to the frame output
  + [leading] is carrying the dominant pressure for the current question
  + [blocking] is stopping promotion, action, archive, or integration until a fault is resolved

  = must: keep depth visible when faculty contribution affects output
  = must: allow depth to rise or fall as the focal subject changes
  = must: treat blocking as a disposition, not as proof of final truth

& [BalanceAxisSet] is the retained paired structure inside the unified field
  + [truth_integrity_axis] is Honesty and Security balancing truth, representation, identity integrity, authority, and safety
  + [memory_clarity_axis] is Archivist and Refiner balancing preservation, provenance, clutter, compression, and focus clarity
  + [direction_integration_axis] is Planner and Weaver balancing goal-serving path, dependency order, component relation, and coherent fit
  + [wisdom_caution_axis] is Wisdom and Caution balancing meaning, good judgment, consequence, restraint, uncertainty, and warning

  = must: use axes as interrogation geometry, not as separate dispatch queues
  = must: let axis pressure modify the depth profile for its facets
  = must: preserve cross-axis tension when one axis recommends promotion and another recommends probe, defer, or block

& [UnifiedInterrogationCycle] is the operating pass for faculty attention
  + [input] is focal_subject, active_question, entry_cue, periphery_state, evidence_state, authority_boundary, and action_need
  + [output] is depth_profile, faculty_findings, axis_tension, unified_disposition, promotion_status, next_step_candidate, and residual_outside

  = step_1: open one UnifiedFacultyAttention frame
  = step_2: identify focal_subject, active_question, authority boundary, and outside
  = step_3: assign an initial depth_profile from entry_cue and visible pressure
  = step_4: interrogate through all faculty facets at their assigned depth
  = step_5: raise depth for any facet that detects contradiction, boundary risk, missing record support, clutter, route pressure, relation pressure, wisdom yield, or caution debt
  = step_6: reconcile balance axes and cross-axis tension
  = step_7: emit unified_disposition with only the faculty findings needed to explain the result
  = step_8: preserve residual outside and route depth changes to focal state, registry state, manager state, periphery stream, or task output

& [FacultyFacetResponsibilities] is the compact role map for the unified field
  + [Honesty] is truth status, fair representation, evidence fit, scope honesty, and unsupported certainty
  + [Security] is identity integrity, authority containment, safe boundary line, action admissibility, and breach risk
  + [Archivist] is source preservation, provenance, narrative continuity, record pointers, and reentry support
  + [Refiner] is focus cleanliness, compression, clutter reduction, edge sharpening, and periphery routing
  + [Planner] is goal-serving intention blend, dependency order, route candidates, readiness, and next step
  + [Weaver] is relation, coherence, integrated shape, protected distinction, fit, and fabric continuity
  + [Wisdom] is meaning, proportionality, judgment, priority, value, and integration maturity
  + [Caution] is uncertainty, consequence, warning, restraint, hidden risk, and false promotion prevention

  = must: let responsibilities overlap only through named axis tension
  = must: keep each reported finding tied to the faculty facet that produced it

& [DepthWeightedActivationPolicy] is the rule preventing output flood
  + [reporting_threshold] is a faculty reports when it changes truth, safety, memory, clarity, direction, integration, wisdom, caution, or outside
  + [quiet_success] is a faculty remains ambient or watch because it found no disposition-changing pressure
  + [depth_raise_trigger] is contradiction, boundary risk, source gap, clutter load, route conflict, integration mismatch, meaning pressure, caution warning, or user emphasis
  + [depth_lower_trigger] is resolved tension, no new pressure, stable periphery, or sufficient disposition

  = must: report quiet_success only when absence of pressure matters to the frame
  = must: raise depth rather than create a separate frame when a faculty becomes important
  = must: lower depth when a faculty no longer changes the disposition
  - never: emit repetitive faculty reports merely to prove activation

(unified_faculty_attention) :entry_cue: /unified_attention_boundary/ |unresolved_faculty_residual|
  + [entry_cue] is the first visible reason faculty attention activates
  + [unified_attention_boundary] is one attention frame containing all faculty facets, depth profile, balance axes, source boundary, and outside
  + [unresolved_faculty_residual] is any faculty pressure not resolved at current depth
  = inside: faculty field, depth profile, balance axes, faculty findings, axis tension, unified disposition, and promotion status
  = boundary: focal subject, active question, source evidence, authority, periphery, action need, and outside preservation
  |outside| hidden native attention, equal-noise activation, unsupported promotion, unresolved faculty pressure, unrelated workspace changes, and exact model internals

& [SurfaceInquiryMarker_UnifiedFacultyAttention] is the deeper-inquiry marker for this surface
  + [surface_key] is unified_faculty_attention
  + [surface_file] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\UnifiedFacultyAttention.sop
  + [inquiry_term_set] is depth_profile, faculty_field, balance_axis_set, shared_pair_frame, direction_integration_axis, unified_interrogation_cycle, depth_weighted_activation, wisdom_caution_axis, periphery_state, semantic_lookup, semantic_hash_index, traversal, latent_depth, periphery_dimensional_probe, unresolved_faculty_residual, and router
  + [lookup_table] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\indexes\SurfacePeripheryInquiryTable.sop
  + [lookup_ready_terms] is depth_profile, faculty_field, balance_axis_set, shared_pair_frame, direction_integration_axis, wisdom_caution_axis, periphery_state, semantic_lookup, semantic_hash_index, traversal, latent_depth, and periphery_dimensional_probe
  + [unresolved_inquiry_set] is router

  = must: use SurfacePeripheryInquiryIndex before expanding this surface into deeper files
  = must: keep unresolved router inquiry outside until a router contract exists
  = should: query lookup_table by surface_key and inquiry_term before broad repository search
